======
RULES
======



(was passiert, wenn man in der mitte ist? -_-)

(2x1 -> 1x1 )

right [ > player  | blob_l | blob_r ] -> [ > player |  | blob ] sfx2
left [ > player  | blob_r | blob_l ] -> [ > player |  | blob ] sfx2
up [ > player  | blob_d | blob_u ] -> [ > player |  | blob ] sfx2
down [ > player  | blob_u | blob_d ] -> [ > player |  | blob ] sfx2


( (n+1)x1 -> (n)x1 )

right [ > player  | blob_l | blob_h ] -> [ > player | | blob_l ] sfx2
left [ > player  | blob_r | blob_h ] -> [ > player | | blob_r ] sfx2
up [ > player  | blob_d | blob_v ] -> [ > player | | blob_d ] sfx2
down [ > player  | blob_u | blob_v ] ->  [ > player | | blob_u ] sfx2



(1x1 -> 2x1)
right [ no obstacle | < player | blob ] -> [ player | blob_l | blob_r ] sfx1
left [ no obstacle | < player | blob ] -> [ player | blob_r | blob_l ] sfx1
up [ no obstacle | < player | blob ] -> [ player | blob_d | blob_u ] sfx1
down [ no obstacle | < player | blob ] -> [ player | blob_u | blob_d ] sfx1



( (n)x1 -> (n+1)x1)
right [ no obstacle | < player | blob_l ] -> [ player | blob_l | blob_h ] sfx1
left [ no obstacle | < player | blob_r ] -> [ player | blob_r | blob_h ] sfx1
up [ no obstacle | < player | blob_d ] -> [ player | blob_d | blob_v ] sfx1
down [ no obstacle | < player | blob_u ] -> [ player | blob_u | blob_v ] sfx1


([ > player | blob ] -> [ > player | > blob ])

[ > goostuff | wall ] -> cancel

